{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You are the analyst for TST-001: FS-RBAC-03 Live RBAC Enforcement.\n\n## Your Task\nRead the rolling context pack at `aidd/reports/context/TST-001.pack.md` and the PRD at `aidd/docs/prd/TST-001.prd.md`. \n\nThe user has already provided answers to all analyst questions:\n- Q1=B: All mutation APIs (POST/PUT/DELETE) require RBAC control\n- Q2=B: Current implementation is custom middleware on JWT-claims\n- Q3=A: Frontend uses React + Context/Redux\n- Q4=A: Audit logs go to database (separate table)\n- Q5=A: Session sync uses WebSocket (push updates)\n\n## Your Output\n1. Review the PRD sections and update/improve based on the answers\n2. Fill in sections that reference the answers (Overview, Context, Goals, etc.)\n3. Ensure the PRD is consistent with the analyst responses\n4. Update the AIDD:RESEARCH_HINTS section with specific paths/keywords for the researcher stage\n5. Set the PRD Status to \"READY\" if all required fields are complete\n\nDo NOT ask the user questions - the answers are already provided. Focus on synthesizing the PRD content based on the given answers."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"tool_ynIVCQem7L99hNZtqnm4S7Qz","session_id":"8bf45a30-ee14-4cd7-b180-00fa1c43e905","uuid":"1fc83f72-c8cf-4dfd-b66f-1f30f1036a3e"}
