ynthesis of Analyst Answers\n| Question | Answer | Impact on PRD |\n|----------|--------|---------------|\n| Q1 | B (All mutation APIs) | Scope covers POST/PUT/DELETE endpoints |\n| Q2 | B (Custom JWT middleware) | Extend existing middleware, not replace |\n| Q3 | A (React + Context/Redux) | Frontend integration uses Redux state |\n| Q4 | A (Database table) | Audit logs stored in DB with retention |\n| Q5 | A (WebSocket push) | Real-time sync via WebSocket |"}],"totalDurationMs":292917,"totalTokens":31437,"totalToolUseCount":23,"usage":{"input_tokens":335,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":30464,"output_tokens":638,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
